UID:JQbEkJSmIdhqsLEid9cQZ
SUMMARY:Kickstands Up! All Motorcycle Club Day
DTSTAMP:20260413T004137Z
DTSTART:20260425T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Inviting all motorcycle clubs to roll on down to MOHAI! Indicat
	e your Motorcycle Cub membership and receive $5 off admission all day\\\, 
	and explore Kickstands Up: 125 Years of Motorcycling in the Pacific Northw
	est with gallery talks by exhibit co-curators from the Pacific Northwest M
	useum of Motorcycling from 2-4pm. \\nSpots are limited and are assigned on
	 a first-come\\\, first-served basis. \\nFor accessibility support\\\, ple
	ase contact programs@mohai.org two weeks before the event.\n\nhttps://moha
	i.org/event/kickstands-up-all-motorcycle-club-day/\n\nFrom MOHAI - Museum 
